### USERS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

###

### Create a user profile (called after Supabase Auth signup)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Test Customer",
  "phone": "0311-9876543",
  "email": "customer@test.com",
  "home_area": "DHA"
}


### Health Check
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/health

### -----------------------------------------------------
### AUTH — Step 1: Login to get JWT access_token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@digitalkaam.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Step 2: Chat with AI (replace YOUR_TOKEN with access_token from login)
# @name chatRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "sessionId": "session-abc-001",
  "message": "I need an electrician in Gulshan"
}

### Step 3: View full message history for a session
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/history?sessionId=session-abc-001
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### View all past sessions for this user
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/history
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

